{"tid":2000692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西環實要佢輸 涂謹申應該回防地區直選？","createTime":"2020-05-04T04:46:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T07:28:21.000Z","uid":13745,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"2a28a93b0bd9e2e89962e7927ac244497b612d2d","tid":2000692,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知立法會議員黎講邊個最資深？<br />\n涂謹申係咪第一？ 第二係咪臭坑出臭草？<br />\n如果係佢應該有著數<br />\n選主席係最資深嘅議員主持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果涂謹申選超區墮馬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以涂謹申上次為左保鄺神爭D輸<br />\n就算西環唔搞野 分分鐘係輸自己配票<br />\n西環有資源做實時戰報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你泛民得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘西環放流料擾敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n泛民輸一個唔緊要 但係唔好輸最關鍵嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以為左顧全大局<br />\n涂謹申係咪應該返地區直選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又或者超級區議員二合一名單選涂謹申排第一實贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d23e5689be5b575c8ebeaa82ad2b081316b263bc","tid":2000692,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:48:44.000Z","msg":"尹兆堅上超區？"},{"pid":"19121bc7bd76e39d1e6462ba51cfd4b62ca84f20","tid":2000692,"uid":83228,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-