y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03362f053f12add503b6c8d473d767bebfcc21fa","tid":2000692,"uid":278570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T04:59:22.000Z","msg":"今次西環好似淨係出兩個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72429832d7896f85be6562c5d782ea8cfe3ef1aa","tid":2000692,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"條友做過乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墮馬反而係正常。"},{"pid":"a7ec94ff6a96d5cc625561c3c688d28d7274a357","tid":2000692,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72429832d7896f85be6562c5d782ea8cfe3ef1aa","tid":2000692,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"條友做過乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墮馬反而係正常。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"無 含淚都要投"},{"pid":"506f9762392604430afa1dbe6c074f646ecd9a11","tid":2000692,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7ec94ff6a96d5cc625561c3c688d28d7274a357","tid":2000692,"uid":110719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"72429832d7896f85be6562c5d782ea8cfe3ef1aa","tid":2000692,"uid":183881,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"條友做過乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n墮馬反而係正常。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:06:13.000Z","msg":"無 含淚都要投"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"繼續情緒勒索咪睇下到時結果係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfb4631b3f74e63fa7a2ae377b1a0145b393bc8","tid":2000692,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T05:09:46.000Z","msg":"佢呢啲中國民主派議員應該退選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287c596353e951d79e69c505f4e4f3408554f27f","tid":2000692,"uid":12086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,